verbose_text: Interestingly, Zhou and Tsang 's group XREF_BIBR found that the blue/UV UC luminescence of CaF 2 : Yb, Tm can be significantly enhanced by epitaxial growth of an inert alpha-NaYF 4 shell layer and further enhanced by an active alpha-NaYF 4 : Yb shell layer.
